OL,3,CTwo in their seventies arrested after
OL,4,Csuspicious death of elderly woman
OL,6,FPolice in Lincolnshire have arrested
OL,7,Ftwo people in their seventies in
OL,8,Fconnection with a suspicious death.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to an address on
OL,11,FSandringham Way in Sleaford at around
OL,12,F2am on Sunday 22 March where they
OL,13,Ffound the body of an elderly woman.
OL,15,FA 75-year-old woman and a 74-year-old
OL,16,Fman have been arrested.
OL,18,FLincolnshire Police said: "We are in
OL,19,Fthe very early stages of the
OL,20,Finvestigation and will be in the area
OL,21,Ffor some time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
