OL,6,F"Members of the public may see several
OL,7,Fpolice vehicles as a result of our
OL,8,Fenquiries, which we know can cause
OL,9,Fanxiety."
OL,11,FThey added that this is part of the
OL,12,Finvestigative process and the public
OL,13,Fshould not be alarmed.
